# Security Reviewer (reminder)

When editing these files, keep security in mind. For a full vulnerability review, invoke the **security-reviewer** subagent.

## Quick checklist

- **Backend:** Parameterized queries only; no secrets in code or logs; validate and sanitize input; auth checks on protected routes; secure session/token handling.
- **Frontend:** No secrets in client code; no raw user content in HTML; use httpOnly cookies for tokens when possible; avoid sensitive data in URLs or localStorage when avoidable.
- **Config:** Secrets only in env; `.env` never committed; `.env.example` documents variables without values.

For a dedicated security pass, ask the main agent to delegate to **security-reviewer**.
